==Russian==
===Verb===
'''читать''' (čitát’) (''[[impf.]]'', ''transitive'' and ''intransitive'')

# to [[read]]
# to [[recite]]
# to [[lecture]], give a lecture, deliver a lecture
# to [[teach]]

